OL,3,CThe Welsh college that 'could turn a
OL,4,Cmilkman into a professor of economics'
OL,6,FA short stroll from Harlech castle
OL,7,Fstands a cluster of old buildings that
OL,8,Ftell a radical tale.
OL,10,FToday, they stand silent, but they
OL,11,Fwere once home to an experiment that
OL,12,Fchanged lives.
OL,14,FIt was Coleg Harlech. For generations
OL,15,Fof men and women it proved
OL,16,Ftransformative.
