OL,3,CThe Welsh college that 'could turn a
OL,4,Cmilkman into a professor of economics'
OL,6,FThe college opened its doors in 1927
OL,7,Fand offered students from Wales and
OL,8,Faround the world something priceless
OL,9,Fand precious: access to higher
OL,10,Feducation without having to pay.
OL,12,FThe centrepiece of Coleg Harlech was a
OL,13,Fgrand Georgian building that was once
OL,14,Fthe holiday home of an eccentric
OL,15,Fmillionaire.
OL,17,FIt became well known as a "second
OL,18,Fchance" college, often for people who
OL,19,Fhad previously been unable to further
OL,20,Ftheir education for economic or social
OL,21,Freasons.
