OL,3,CThe Welsh college that 'could turn a
OL,4,Cmilkman into a professor of economics'
OL,6,FSheila Maxwell is a former bursar at
OL,7,FColeg Harlech. "The students just knew
OL,8,Fthat there was more in them and they
OL,9,Fwanted to do something for themselves.
OL,10,FSo, a milkman from Wrexham could
OL,11,Fbecome a professor of economics.
OL,13,F"It was like a door that was ajar, and
OL,14,Fas you came to the college you widened
OL,15,Fthat doorway out into a full
OL,16,Feducation."
OL,18,FBut running a residential college was
OL,19,Fexpensive, and as the years went on
OL,20,Fthose costs began to soar.
