OL,3,CThe Welsh college that 'could turn a
OL,4,Cmilkman into a professor of economics'
OL,6,FThe education system was changing too.
OL,7,FColeg Harlech had to fight hard to
OL,8,Fattract students and funding.
OL,10,FThe college finally closed in 2017.
OL,11,FThe imposing buildings stand empty,
OL,12,Fawaiting a new lease of life.
